videos.description: Terry Swanson finds the end zone from a yard out to give the Rockets an early 10-0 lead.
videos.headline: Swanson scores Toledo's first TD of season

videos.description: Toledo converts on fourth down on Cody Thompson's 22-yard reception over the middle.
videos.headline: Woodside finds Thompson for 4th Down conversion

videos.description: Kahlil Robinson adjusts mid-coverage to intercept Davis Cheek's throw.
videos.headline: Robinson dives to pick off Elon pass

videos.description: Brelynd Cyphers' 9-yard run up the middle gives the Phoenix their first points of the year.
videos.headline: Cyphers runs it in for Elon's first TD of season

videos.description: Diontae Johnson starts the second half with a bang, returning a kickoff 99 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Johnson takes kickoff 99 yards to the house to start second half

videos.description: Terry Swanson eludes Elon's defense and stretches out to score on the 5-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Swanson dives into end zone for second TD of game

videos.description: Reggie Gilliam's 1-yard touchdown run through the middle puts Toledo up 40-7.
videos.headline: Toledo's Gilliam runs it in to extend lead

videos.description: Malcolm Summers converts goal line carry for Elon's second rushing score of the game.
videos.headline: Summers pounds it in for 1-yard TD run

videos.description: Trevon Mathis' pass is cut off and picked off by Greg Liggs Jr., who then returns it 19 yards.
videos.headline: Liggs Jr. jumps route and intercepts pass

videos.description: Shakif Seymour breaks multiple tackles to pick up big yardage.
videos.headline: Seymour bursts through the defense for big 44-yard run

videos.description: Shakif Seymour puts the exclamation mark on Toledo's 47-13 win.
videos.headline: Seymour's 9-yard TD run caps Toledo's offensive explosion
